title: Elqueeness
description: When Ji-Hoon’s unfortunate life is tragically cut short, he is met with the revelation that he is another world’s Water Spirit King mistakenly born on Earth. Many trials await him as the new ‘Elqueeness’ in the fantastic world of Arkadon. Will he be able to forge new bonds and joyful memories, or will he be dragged into despair as a dark threat to his new world, life and companions is brewing?
author: 이환
